window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Best-selling author C. J. Box—an Anthony and Macavity Award winner—earned starred reviews from both <i>Publishers Weekly</i> and <i>Booklist</i> for this exceptional mystery. Taking advantage of a legal loophole, a lawyer kills four people in Yellowstone National Park and walks away a free man. As the public outcry intensifies, the governor hires former game warden Joe Pickett to conduct a private investigation.</p>"; 
